languages.text: "Посмотри на себя, ничтожество. Чем ты стал. Нам пророчили величие, но ты выбрал утопать в самоутешениях и лжи".

traits.locale_text: "Посмотри на себя, ничтожество. Посмотри чем ты стал. Нам пророчили величие, великое будущее. Но ты выбрал утопать в самоутешениях и лжи".

languages.text: "Look at yourself. At what you have become. Pathetic. They said we were destined for greatness, but you have chosen to wallow in self-pity and lies."
languages.original_text: "Посмотри на себя, ничтожество. Чем ты стал. Нам пророчили величие, но ты выбрал утопать в самоутешениях и лжи".

languages.text: «Mírate al espejo. Mira en qué te has convertido. Patético. Dijeron que estábamos destinados a la grandeza, pero tú has preferido rebozarte en la autocompasión y la mentira».

languages.text: 「自分を見てみろ。今の自分の姿を。哀れだな。私達は偉大になる運命だと言葉をもらったが、貴様は被害妄想と嘘に溺れる道を選んだ」
languages.original_text: "Look at yourself. At what you have become. Pathetic. They said we were destined for greatness, but you have chosen to wallow in self-pity and lies."

languages.text: “看看你这个样子吧，看看你变成了什么样子，真是可悲。他们说我们注定会成就一番伟业，可你却只会顾影自怜，沉湎于谎言之中。”
languages.original_text: "Look at yourself. At what you have become. Pathetic. They said we were destined for greatness, but you have chosen to wallow in self-pity and lies."

languages.text: "Seht Euch an. Was aus Euch geworden ist. Erbärmlich. Es hieß, Ihr wäret zu Großem bestimmt, doch stattdessen habt Ihr entschieden, Euch in Selbstmitleid und Lügen zu suhlen."
languages.original_text: "Look at yourself. At what you have become. Pathetic. They said we were destined for greatness, but you have chosen to wallow in self-pity and lies."

languages.text: « Regardez-vous. Regardez ce que vous êtes devenu. C'est pitoyable. On nous disait destinés à de grandes choses, mais vous avez préféré vous complaire dans l'apitoiement et les mensonges. »

languages.text: "Kendine, neye dönüştüğüne baksana. Acınası haldesin. Yazgımızda yüceliğin yattığını söylemişlerdi. Sense kendine acıyıp yalanlara gömülmeyi seçtin."
languages.original_text: "Look at yourself. At what you have become. Pathetic. They said we were destined for greatness, but you have chosen to wallow in self-pity and lies."
